Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.74,0:00:41.33,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ONE PIECE!!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.37,0:00:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All of us, I ask you travelers{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.37,0:00:43.96,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All of us tabibito ni tsugu{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are your dreams still pure?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:47.25,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sono yume wa mada nigoccha inai ka?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.38,0:00:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sleepless cells are shaken and burst{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.38,0:00:55.72,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nemurenai saibou ga kusugurare hajiketeku{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.76,0:01:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still, all of us, in the middle of an adventure{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.76,0:01:02.47,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima mo All of us bouken no tochuu{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.52,0:01:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All of us, I tell you travelers{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.52,0:01:04.98,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All of us tabibito e tsugu{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.02,0:01:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No such thing as a pointless fight{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.02,0:01:08.77,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}imi no nai tatakai wa nain da{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.57,0:01:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When random contexts{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.57,0:01:12.90,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}barabara no bunmyaku ga{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.94,0:01:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Start to make sense on their own{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.94,0:01:16.86,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ishi wo mochi tsunagareba{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.91,0:01:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The threads of time are spun back together{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.91,0:01:23.29,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}toki no ito ga tsumugi naosareru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.62,0:01:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The world keeps changing along with us{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.62,0:01:28.83,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ore tachi to tomoni sekai kawari tsuzuketeru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.88,0:01:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(All of us) us, us{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.88,0:01:31.38,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(All of us) a-su, a-su{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.42,0:01:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(Dream save us us) us, all of us{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.42,0:01:36.76,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(Dream save us us) a-su, All of us{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.52,0:01:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Run, Koby!\NA Desperate Escape Strategy!"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.12,0:02:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.28,0:02:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I won again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.83,0:02:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys sure have a lot of free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.91,0:02:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the keys to the cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.84,0:02:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.80,0:02:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.10,0:02:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold your tongue, you fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.98,0:02:35.07,Italics,,0,0,0,,PERONA, HOLLOW-HOLLOW FRUIT,\NGHOST PRINCESS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.53,0:02:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.11,0:02:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a lot of nerve, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.53,0:02:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is "Shut up" easier for you to understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kneel down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Negative...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.21,0:02:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...Hollow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.46,0:02:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Negative! Negative!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.67,0:03:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Negative! Negative!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.10,0:03:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry that\NI have less courage than a water flea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.07,0:03:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna quit pirating\Nand live quietly in a prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.45,0:03:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I got them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.12,0:03:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all out of spirit...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.33,0:04:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.16,0:04:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch. Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.14,0:04:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.94,0:04:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the one they call Koby the hero?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.53,0:04:42.78,Italics,,0,0,0,,KOBY, NAVY HQ CAPTAIN (SWORD)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.11,0:04:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You got captured!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.74,0:04:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,For a supposed hero,\Nyou're below expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.37,0:04:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.21,0:04:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help you out,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.25,0:04:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,so free Moria-{\i1}sama {\i}who is being held\Nin a cell further in from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.13,0:05:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Moria?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.01,0:05:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Gecko Moria is here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.64,0:05:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you telling me to collaborate\Nwith pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.06,0:05:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right!\NMoria-{\i1}sama{\i}'s life is at risk!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.40,0:05:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a Navy soldier...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.45,0:05:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Gecko Moria is a pirate...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Free him, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.58,0:05:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I have big news!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Koby has escaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:41.63,Italics,,0,0,0,,PIRATE ISLAND OF BEEHIVE, NEW WORLD
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.54,0:05:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.42,0:05:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that he's escaped,\Nhe's no longer Commodore's quarry, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.55,0:05:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How much will we get if we capture him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.18,0:05:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeehaw!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.81,0:05:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we don't need to put a bounty on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Cross Guild will pay for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.10,0:06:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought odds on him with a Win ticket!\NThe payout is gonna be big!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How much will we get if we kill him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna be surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.24,0:06:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,His bounty is five stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That means five treasure chests!\NThat's about 500 million berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,His bounty is five stars?!\NA captain's bounty is usually one star!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Let's hit the jackpot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.76,0:06:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The hunting begins now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.11,0:06:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone! We're almost there.\NHang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Koby-{\i1}san{\i},\Nthank you for saving slaves like us...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on. Don't call yourself a slave!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.29,0:07:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all unfortunate victims\Nwho were captured by pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a Navy soldier,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll save you all at any cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.43,0:07:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Pizarro-{\i1}san{\i}! What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.73,0:07:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel a tickle\Non the left side of my chest-{\i1}meow{\i}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.86,0:07:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where slaves are held\Nbefore the sale...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they breaking out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The slaves escaped?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we hunt them all, Pizarro-{\i1}san{\i}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly! You guys are so savage!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring them all back! Don't even kill Koby!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Or I'll tell Teach!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does that rock talk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.73,0:08:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He knows that we're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.23,0:08:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.27,0:08:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.44,0:08:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.70,0:08:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Just run away before we slow you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.24,0:08:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be the bait,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.29,0:08:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,so make sure you all get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.34,0:08:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.21,0:08:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll meet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.76,0:08:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Captain Koby...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.89,0:08:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a saint!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:48.36,Italics,,0,0,0,,PRISON
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.94,0:08:55.74,Italics,,0,0,0,,SHIRYU OF THE RAIN\NCLEAR-CLEAR FRUIT, INVISIBLE MAN
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.11,0:09:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you capture them yourself,\NPizarro?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.62,0:09:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Teach will get mad at me later!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:10.67,Italics,,0,0,0,,"THE CORRUPT KING" AVALO PIZARRO\NISLE-ISLE FRUIT, ISLAND-MAN
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.80,0:09:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Because whenever I move,\NI end up breaking things-{\i1}meow{\i}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.18,0:09:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Vasco Shot. What are you gonna do-{\i1}meow{\i}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.69,0:09:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If I set the town on fire,\Nthey'll have nowhere to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.11,0:09:37.32,Italics,,0,0,0,,"HEAVY DRINKER" VASCO SHOT\NGLUG-GLUG FRUIT, BOOZE-MAN
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.08,0:09:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't do that!\NThat would be a huge fire-{\i1}meow{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.63,0:09:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Teach would get pissed-{\i1}meow{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem. Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No-{\i1}meow{\i}!\NWe just finished repairing Rocky Port!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you rather leave it to Wolf?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.85,0:10:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolf?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.14,0:10:12.23,Italics,,0,0,0,,"THE GIANT BATTLESHIP" SANJUAN WOLF\NHUGE-HUGE FRUIT, GIGANTIFICATION-MAN
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's out of the question-{\i1}meow{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole town will be gone-{\i1}meow{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.29,0:10:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I need...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to buy more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.39,0:10:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did that bastard go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.77,0:10:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go that way, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.85,0:10:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.19,0:10:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you look cute and docile,\Nbut you're surprisingly bold...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:10:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.49,0:11:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you don't have to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.45,0:11:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'll get a lot of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.87,0:11:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Five Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.45,0:11:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I found him! Right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! They found me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.43,0:11:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! I guess I can't outrun them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.14,0:11:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.18,0:11:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to somehow keep luring them\Nuntil everyone else goes out to sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.09,0:12:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.55,0:12:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Koby the hero!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.52,0:12:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Koby the hero,\NI want to turn this island...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.19,0:12:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...this Pirate Island...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.03,0:12:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...into a full-fledged nation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.95,0:12:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A World Government-affiliated nation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.38,0:12:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the king!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.22,0:12:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Blackbeard Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.01,0:12:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.02,0:12:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.39,0:12:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way it'd be accepted!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.27,0:12:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a country of criminals!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.36,0:13:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't ruin someone else's dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll negotiate with them\Nusing you as a bargaining chip.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.91,0:13:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If the Government and the Navy start negotiating\Nwith terrorists, we're doomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:16.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,JUSTICE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're wasting your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.46,0:13:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm a member of SWORD!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.88,0:13:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sword? What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.43,0:13:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't gonna go well.\NGive up on the trade, Teach.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.98,0:13:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,SWORD...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.86,0:13:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.36,0:13:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...he's a Navy soldier but also not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.58,0:13:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He surrendered his Navy Code.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:13:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,SWORD is a group of...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.38,0:14:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...Navy soldiers\Nwho have submitted their resignations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.67,0:14:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So they can pick a fight with the Four Emperors\Nwithout permission from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They can also do whatever they like\Nand disregard any orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.26,0:14:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They're wild-card commandoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.48,0:14:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,In exchange,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the Navy is in no way responsible\Nfor their actions
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.94,0:14:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and can fire them anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.28,0:14:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.33,0:14:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the difference between the half-wits\Nwho are waiting for permission to fight us
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.54,0:14:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and the ones who just charge in\Nwithout a care in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.46,0:14:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I like that style. I get it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.38,0:14:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.55,0:14:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm not gonna change my plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.56,0:14:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you're a SWORD member,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.44,0:15:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,people call you a hero,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.94,0:15:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,so I wonder if the Navy\Ncan stick to the decision of abandoning you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.24,0:15:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask the public!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the Government\Ncan't remain unblemished!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Until then, lock him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let him escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.71,0:15:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here! Koby!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I cooperated with a pirate...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.52,0:15:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But necessity knows no law!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.69,0:15:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of keeping guard,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.16,0:15:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna hunt a Five Star, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.25,0:16:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.75,0:16:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope those who escaped are all fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.76,0:16:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Three Navy soldiers showed up at the port!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Navy soldiers?! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.97,0:16:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They're strong! Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.73,0:16:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did someone come to rescue me?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.94,0:16:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, no! How arrogant I am!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.90,0:16:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel ashamed!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are they?! Why are they so strong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:16:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They're heading towards\Nthe center of the town!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.14,0:16:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What do they want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.22,0:17:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How would I know?! Stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.23,0:17:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Guns don't work on them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.15,0:17:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.70,0:17:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,His head got cut off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.87,0:17:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I took one down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That serves you right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.88,0:17:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.30,0:17:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Logia type?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.43,0:17:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with him?!\NHis body's like clay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Koby?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.61,0:17:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't those buildings moving?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.36,0:18:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No, stupid! They're not!\NYou drink too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.83,0:18:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Be a good little boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.38,0:18:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Move forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.17,0:18:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a strange woman. Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.14,0:18:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Brace up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.27,0:18:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You look pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.56,0:18:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Come on! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,She's whipping a building...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.44,0:18:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you staring at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,S-She's a Navy soldier?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.79,0:18:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How rare is it to see a Navy soldier\Nwhen you're a pirate?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.00,0:18:53.34,Italics,,0,0,0,,KUJAKU, NAVY HQ REAR ADMIRAL (SWORD)\NGRANDDAUGHTER OF GREAT ADVISER TSURU\NWHIP-WHIP FRUIT, DISCIPLINE-WOMAN
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.46,0:18:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here. You're so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.56,0:19:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll discipline you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.98,0:19:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're cornered, Koby!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! I'm surrounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.20,0:19:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Take aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.33,0:19:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.59,0:19:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's in place!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.02,0:19:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be ready soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me, my beloved pupil!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How far I have run{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:21.17,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}doredake hashitte kita noka{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Without knowing it, I counted scars{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:28.47,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}wakaranai mama kizuato kazoeta{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.93,0:20:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A treasure map in my head all along{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.93,0:20:35.90,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}zutto atama no naka ni aru takara no chizu{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still looking for the future{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:42.40,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mirai wo sagashi tsuzuketeru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.45,0:20:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The real promise{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.45,0:20:49.12,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hontou no yakusoku wa{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lies much deeper in my heart{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:56.29,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mune no oku no motto oku ni aru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:21:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A dream that no one can catch up with{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:21:05.43,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}dare mo mina oitsukenai yume{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's all I hold on to{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:11.14,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitotsu dakishimete{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To you who smiles like the sun{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:18.23,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}taiyou no youni warau anata e{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll sing the same song as that day{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:25.15,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ano hi to onaji uta wo utau yo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This wish I don't want to forget even when I grow up{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:32.20,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}otona ni nattemo wasuretakunai{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Until it reaches you{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:39.67,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kono negai ga todoku made{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.43,0:21:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Dive into the Sea of Information!\NThe Punk Records Library!"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.10,0:21:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, I'm Lilith, one of the Satellites of\NDr. Vegapunk, the genius scientist!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.85,0:22:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Edison, also Vegapunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.07,0:22:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Today we'll introduce this one! Koby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.65,0:22:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a Navy captain and\Na member of SWORD, a Top Secret Special Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.16,0:22:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He is called "Koby the hero"!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.66,0:22:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He was born on May 13th and\Nlikes buttered potatoes and Rika's onigiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.29,0:22:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Once, while being imprisoned by pirates\Nand forced to work like a horse, he met Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.79,0:22:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He was encouraged by Luffy\Nand successfully got away from the pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.26,0:22:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,After Captain Morgan's incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.14,0:22:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,he enlisted in the Navy, which he had\Ndreamed of doing since he was a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.68,0:22:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Since he is kind-hearted, he couldn't bear\Nthe loss of so many lives during the Paramount War,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.11,0:22:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and his desperate action\Nled to the end of the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.28,0:22:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We're wasting people's lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.41,0:22:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He continued to train himself,\Nsaved civilians in the Rocky Port Incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.20,0:22:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and rose to the rank of captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.83,0:23:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But now he has been abducted by Blackbeard...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.67,0:23:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Will he be able to escape\Nfrom the Pirate Island of Beehive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.21,0:23:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.13,0:23:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you've seen it,\Ndonate to our research fund!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.76,0:23:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,See you next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.52,0:23:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A huge warship comes flying down from the sky!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.10,0:23:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The man who is standing on its bow\Nis the hero of the Navy, Vice Admiral Garp!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.78,0:23:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To save the cornered Koby, he tightens his fist!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.11,0:23:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A giant, deeply-felt blow is thrown down\Non the chaotic Beehive!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.08,0:23:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.87,0:23:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,"For the Beloved Pupil -\NThe Fist of Vice Admiral Garp!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.46,0:23:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
